This is implementaion for the following paper:- Improved Decremental Algorithms for maintaining transitive closure and All-pairs Shortest paths" by Baswana, Hariharan, and Sen

Compile the code using makefile

Graph is input in following format: 	
first line contains two integer n(number of vertices) and m(number of edges), each of m subsequnet lines contains two integers describing the edge between two vertices.

After taking graph as a input, there are 3 options:
1) Delete edge   2) are u and v in same component ?  3) exit


